cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

The paper discusses a model of cortical processing of visual stimuli, which is a topic closely related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions mechanisms of feature extraction and connectivity between cells, which are topics related to neural networks (cs.NE). The proposed method of spectral clustering with anisotropic affinities is a machine learning technique (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the discussion of neural plausibility suggests a connection to systems and control (cs.SY).
